---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
const IMG = "https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663540279873/mqBaZEe8cowVKqLebSdcGQ/hawley-hero-kitchen-mSpoc3xtKks8iMHpTCvAxs.webp";
const schemaData = [{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "Kitchen Remodel Cost in St. Petersburg FL (2025 Guide)",
  "datePublished": "2025-03-15",
  "author": {"@type": "Person", "name": "Landon Hawley"},
  "publisher": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "Hawley Construction Co.", "url": "https://hawleyconstruction.co"},
  "image": IMG,
  "url": "https://hawleyconstruction.co/blog/kitchen-remodel-cost-st-petersburg-2025"
}];
---
<Layout
  title="Kitchen Remodel Cost in St. Petersburg FL (2025 Guide) | Hawley Construction"
  description="A detailed breakdown of what a kitchen remodel costs in St. Petersburg, FL in 2025 — from a basic refresh to a full custom renovation. Real project examples included."
  canonical="https://hawleyconstruction.co/blog/kitchen-remodel-cost-st-petersburg-2025"
  schema={schemaData}
  ogImage={IMG}
>
  <Navbar />
  <section class="pt-28 pb-12 md:pt-36 md:pb-16" style="background-color:var(--navy);">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs mb-6" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">
        <a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">Home</a><span>/</span>
        <a href="/blog" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">Blog</a><span>/</span>
        <span style="color:var(--gold);">Kitchen Remodel Cost</span>
      </nav>
      <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-3 block" style="color:var(--gold);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">Kitchen Remodeling</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight" style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;">Kitchen Remodel Cost in St. Petersburg FL (2025 Guide)</h1>
      <p class="text-sm" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">By Landon Hawley &middot; March 15, 2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24" style="background-color:var(--cream);">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <img src={IMG} alt="Kitchen remodel St. Petersburg FL" class="w-full h-72 object-cover mb-10" style="border-radius:2px;" loading="eager" />
      <div class="prose max-w-none" style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;">
        <p>The most common question we hear from St. Petersburg homeowners is: <strong style="color:var(--navy2);">"What will my kitchen remodel actually cost?"</strong> The honest answer is that it depends — but here is a detailed breakdown based on real projects we have completed in Pinellas County.</p>
        <h2 style="color:var(--navy2);font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">Kitchen Remodel Cost Tiers in St. Petersburg (2025)</h2>
        <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <thead>
            <tr style="background-color:var(--navy);color:white;">
              <th style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;text-align:left;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">Tier</th>
              <th style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;text-align:left;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">Cost Range</th>
              <th style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;text-align:left;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">What Is Included</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid oklch(0.88 0.01 250);">
              <td style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy2);">Refresh</td>
              <td style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;">$30,000 – $50,000</td>
              <td style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;">New countertops, backsplash, paint, lighting, hardware, select cabinet updates</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid oklch(0.88 0.01 250);background-color:white;">
              <td style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy2);">Mid-Range</td>
              <td style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;">$50,000 – $100,000</td>
              <td style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;">Full cabinet replacement, new appliances, flooring, layout adjustments</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid oklch(0.88 0.01 250);">
              <td style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy2);">Premium</td>
              <td style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;">$100,000+</td>
              <td style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;">Custom cabinetry, structural changes, high-end appliances, designer finishes</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <h2 style="color:var(--navy2);font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">What Drives Kitchen Remodel Costs in St. Petersburg?</h2>
        <p><strong style="color:var(--navy2);">Cabinetry</strong> is typically the largest single cost, representing 30-40% of the total budget. Semi-custom cabinetry from brands like KraftMaid runs $15,000-$35,000 installed. Custom cabinetry starts at $30,000 and can exceed $80,000 for a large kitchen.</p>
        <p><strong style="color:var(--navy2);">Countertops</strong> are the second-largest cost. Quartz from Cambria or Caesarstone runs $80-$150 per square foot installed. A standard kitchen with 40 sq ft of countertop costs $3,200-$6,000 for quartz.</p>
        <p><strong style="color:var(--navy2);">Labor</strong> in Pinellas County has increased significantly since 2022. Budget 25-35% of your total project cost for skilled labor including carpentry, plumbing, electrical, and tile work.</p>
        <p><strong style="color:var(--navy2);">Permits</strong> for a kitchen remodel in St. Petersburg typically run $500-$1,500 depending on the scope of work. We include permit costs in our fixed-price quotes.</p>
        <h2 style="color:var(--navy2);font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">How to Get an Accurate Quote</h2>
        <p>The only way to get an accurate kitchen remodel quote is an in-home estimate. We measure your space, discuss your goals and material preferences, and provide a detailed fixed-price proposal within 3-5 business days. There is no charge for the estimate and no obligation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 p-8 text-center" style="background-color:var(--navy);border-radius:2px;">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3" style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;">Get a Free Kitchen Remodel Estimate</h2>
        <p class="mb-6" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">Serving St. Petersburg, Tampa, Clearwater, and all of Tampa Bay.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/kitchen-remodeling-st-petersburg/" class="btn-gold text-center">Kitchen Remodeling</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-outline-light text-center">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
